Product Name: 007 For Women II Eau de Parfum Vaporisateur 75ml
Short Product Description:
What It Is: Women II Eau de Parfum Vaporisateur 75ml

What It Does:

The new oriental - floral composition is lighter in relation to the original. It opens with a combination of pink pepper, pink freesia, raspberry and pink champagne. The fruity character of blackberry is mixed with a floral bouquet of gardenia, pink oleander and black baccarat rose. The oriental and silky base consists of musk, vanilla, cedar, sandalwood and leather. The face of the perfume is the Italian actress Caterina Murino, who played Solange Dimitrios in the 2006 James Bond movie "Casino Royale".The luxuriously carved, diamond- cut glass bottle is now colored in soft pink.

About The Brand:
James Bond 007 for Women II comes out in the spring of 2016, a year after the first feminine fragrance from the James Bond line, James Bond 007 for Women. The first edition supposedly embodies a mysterious Bond lady and her charm, wit and sense of adventure. James Bond 007 for Women II continues the same story line, offering a charming daily variation in response to the evening debut.
Manufacturer Name & Address: BEAUTY IMPEX PRIVATE LIMITED, Coty, 14, Rue Du 4 Septembre, 75002, Paris, France

Product Name: by Titan Women Nude EDP- 50 ML
Short Product Description:
Nude evokes memories of a summer romance.
The first blush of the sparkling lychee and raspberry, with the playfulness of citrusy bergamot, makes way for the sensuous lushness of the rose.
Nude is designed with a hint of musk which makes the memory of that sweet romance last forever.
This elegant and refined creation belongs to the floral fruity, woody family.
From the very first notes, this fragrance reveals a sparkling and original top with touches of lychee blended with natural bergamot and the sweet fizziness of raspberry.
The heart highlights beautiful notes of romantic flowers such as delicate rose petals, and an exclusive natural rose with peachy accents.
This floral bouquet is rendered sublime by jasmine petal notes and the green notes of soft, suave, but powerful violet.
The dense, dry down is composed of a unique succession of woods and spices, exotic sandalwood is mingled with sweet, addictive tonka bean and modern Firmenich musks that embody the whole creation.

The brand continues to be a defining pillar of The Estee Lauder Companies as an industry leader in the men's fragrance and grooming category. Product Name: Men L'Eau Majeure D'Issey Eau de Toilette 100ml
Short Product Description:
What it is:
Eau de Toilette

About the product:
The top notes are fresh bergamot and refreshing grapefruit, with a sparkling accent that evokes images of sunlight glittering on the waves. The middle notes evoke the scent of the sea with a bold, mineral-rich ambergris fragrance. Lively woody notes of cashmeran form the base notes, with a sensual, serene after-scent evoking an image of smooth driftwood washed by the waves. 
L'EAU MAJEURE D'ISSEY is a new men's fragrance inspired by the ferocity of the sea. An aquatic fragrance that combines elegant and sultry scents with a pure ocean scent reminiscent of driftwood in the waves. It evokes an image of "new waves" created by the ceaseless energy of water.
The bottle was designed by American designer Todd Bracher, and evokes an image of the L'EAU D'ISSEY POUR HOMME bottle washed by the waves.

Product Name: Men White Musk Sustainable Eau De Toilette 100 ml
Short Product Description:
White Musk Sustainable Eau De Toilette

Just like a Sunday walk through the woods, our White Musk for Men Eau de Toilette is a breath of fresh air with earthy, sensual notes for an ultra-smooth scent. Fragrance is a pretty powerful thing. Wear too little and it's barely there, wear too much and you're left overpowering the entire room. That's why our White Musk Eau de Toilette is light and subtle enough for every day and lasts as long as the day too. Effortlessly casual, confident and sophisticated, this charming scent features our iconic White Musk fragrance, reinvented for men. It's a clever cocktail of soft and familiar lavender, bold and citrusy geranium, warm and woody cruelty-free musk and smooth and creamy sandalwood. Inspired by White Musk, The Body Shop's Eau de Toilette is just one of many products in our White Musk for Men range. Build up this much-loved scent with our White Musk For Men Hair & Body Wash and our White Musk For Men Anti-Perspirant Deodorant.

What is it?
The innovative and incomparable Original Mercedes-Benz Eau de Toilette is the perfect balance of freshness and sensuality, whose elegance and distinction lies in the marriage of seductive woody notes and magnificent fresh florals. A vibrant, original composition, woody, floral and fresh, reinterpreting and reinforcing the luxurious world of Mercedes-Benz.
Design
The design for the bottle embodies the values that define Mercedes-Benz: perceivable quality, passionate innovation, refined sportiness and distinctive style. The Mercedes-Benz emblem, the three-pointed star, is the symbol that expresses these brand values. Short Product Description: Country of origin southeast Asia, china, indian, bangladesh, nepal, sri lanka, cambodia, thailand, indonesia, malaysia plant part flowers extraction method hydro distilled the Indian kadamba attar is extracted from the flowers of kadam plant. kadam tree is typically found in southeast Asia and particularly in different parts of India. The kadam tree has apricot-gold coloured flowers with a unique and refreshing aroma. the flower of kadam (kadamb) grows during and after the monsoon season in India. Cultural religious significance: the essence of kadam has been appreciated in Hindu culture in India for many centuries. The flower of kadam tree is considered as sacred for Hindu goddesses, mainly goddess durga and lord krishna. The kadamba flower was the emblem of athmallik state, one of the India's princely states during the British rule. What are some key characteristics of kadam attar? Kadam attar is typically woody floral, and oriental in character with a soft touch of honey. It mixes well with pure single-note attars and sandalwood floral water.

Product Name: Women Set of 2 Perfume & Body Mist
Short Product Description:
Set of 2 Perfume & Body Mist
Eternal Radiance is a bright citrusy, floral fragrance that is a tribute to the never-say-die spirit of an eternal optimist.
The fresh top notes of bergamot and mandarin are vibrant and enthralling and act as instant reminders to stay upbeat. The mellow middle notes of geranium, which smell like a rose in lemon shrubs, lend a contemporary green touch to this composition.
Neither too floral, nor too fruity, it smells like bottled sunshine, ready to envelop you in its warmth.
The amiable downto-earth vibe of this perfume is highlighted by the earthy base notes of patchouli and musk.
Serene Bliss - The essence of calm and soothing fluidity is captured in this scent. Inspired by the angelic nature and softness of its muse, the fragrance represents the feeling of entering an enchanted garden.
The top notes of voluptuous Florals and majestic Rose alludes to her peaceful majestic demeanour.
The image of serenity is further stirred as the green Grass notes that intertwine with the salty crispness of a marine accord in the heart of the fragrance.
Its held together with the addictive base notes that are a mix of earthy notes of patchouli, vetiver and moss along with sensual musk and amber.
Manufacturer Name & Address: AJMAL & SONS, SUHAN AEROSAL J/1-8,Radheyshyam Ind. Complex, Asangaon (W) Tal.Shahapur, Dist. Thane, Maharashtra-421601, India

Product Name: Women Set of 2 Perfumes
Short Product Description:
Set of 2
Mythical Bloom - Picture this: refreshing breeze blowing over lush violet fields.
Now lean in, take a whiff and allow the initial effervescence of citrusy bergamot and mandarin to fill up your senses.
The sweet delicacy of blue-violet blooms, the serenity of lavender, and the vibrancy of the crispy citrus, coupled together is a sensation like no other.
When paired with a bouquet of white florals, violets lend a velvety powdery touch to the heart of the perfume thats irresistible and mesmerizing.
Designed to seduce the senses, the warm notes of musk, sandalwood and vanilla anchor the softness of this subtle floral heart.
Magical Maze - The scent of a journey of self-discovery. She is an empowered, globe-trotter, quirky girl who isnt afraid of trying something new.
The sweetness of passion fruit and strawberry in the top notes reflect her amiable nature and the warm, woody and earthy base note reflect her values of staying true to herself while she explores.
And like her heart which seeks harmony, the core of the fragrance delicately balanced, with the cheerful lightness of lily of valley and peony.
Manufacturer Name & Address: AJMAL & SONS, SUHAN AEROSAL, J/1-8,Radheyshyam Ind. Complex, Asangaon (W) Tal.Shahapur, Dist. Thane, Maharashtra-421601, India

Product Name: Women The One Eau de Parfum 75ml
Short Product Description:
What it is:
Like the woman that wears it, the strength and uniqueness of Dolce&Gabbana The One fragrance comes from contrast. Used to adorn pulse points or misted into the air to fall in a scented aura, The One is a modern 'floriental' eau de parfum combining contemporary fruit ingredients with the perfumer's classic palette of white flowers. "Every woman is The One!" Stefano Gabbana.

Features:
Top: The rich Oriental Floral perfume opens with a sparkling and modern interpretation of fresh top notes of zesty Bergamot and Mandarin, combined with juicy Lychee and Peach.
Heart: The journey to the heart of the fragrance follows into the timeless scent of the Madonna Lily with its voluptuous intensity and enveloping femininity.
Base: The fragrance finally unfolds to reveal a deep and sensual base of rich Vanilla and resinous Ambery notes combined with smooth Musky notes to leave a lingering presence

Product Name: Women The Only One Eau de Parfum 100ml
Short Product Description:
What it is:
DOLCE & GABBANA The Only One Eau de Parfum captures the essence of sophisticated and hypnotizing femininity.

What it does:
The Only One's signature lies in the surprising combination of violet and coffee giving life to an enchanting floral scent. Like the woman it represents, the fragrance is an intricate play of opposites. It is from this fusion of the unexpected, a Mocha Violet note, that it draws its appeal.

Fragrance notes:
Top notes: Violet, Bergamot
Heart notes: Coffee, Iris,
Base notes: Vanilla, Patchouli
The violet opens the fragrance, combining with subtle touches of bergamot to create a lively, fresh and juicy bouquet. At the heart, seductive notes of rich coffee are blended with charming iris. Finally, the warm base of vanilla and patchouli lends a tactile, comforting quality, enveloping the senses in an opulent embrace.
